					"type": 23,
					"value": "Three halfling stand near a cart that was once full to the brim with fresh food and supplies. Other refugees swarmed it in a panic and stuffed their pockets - breaking the cart in the process. The halflings got there too later, and now stand next to the wreckage of the cart."
